rows.label: tlk47600165_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahh, feel that breeze...
It reminds me of the time I was riding
on the back of Seiryuu.

rows.label: tlk47600165_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It was a while back now.
The old fellow asked if I'd like to go
on a long-haul journey with him.

rows.label: tlk47600165_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd never been outside the village
before, so it was quite the journey of
discovery, seeing all those islands!

rows.label: tlk47600165_01_msg0004
rows.name:
He asked if I wanted to keep on with it,
but it turned out I got seasick easily,
so I let a certain someone take over.
